                    "content": "<p><strong>Beoordeling Wanted poster</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Aantal punten te verdelen: 0, 3, 5, 7, 8                                            Naam:_______________________<br/>\nTotaal aantal punten te behalen: 80<br/>\n<br/>\nBehaalde punten: _________<br/>\n </p>\n<p> </p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p>Punten:</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-28-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p>Gegevens persoon ingevuld (formulier)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-28-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p>Punt 1 (formulier)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p>Punt 2 (formulier)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p>Punt 3 (formulier)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p>Feitje (formulier)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-30-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p>Netheid (formulier)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p>Poster juist ingevuld</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-314-pixels\">\n<p>Leestekens, zinsopbouw</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"height-29-pixels width-265-pixels\">\n<p> 